properties.SQL select query:
SELECT * FROM GENERATE_SERIES('2022-01-01', '2022-12-31', INTERVAL '1 hour') AS hours
  WHERE hours NOT IN 
  (SELECT (prediction_date + prediction_time)::timestamp  AS time_stamps 
   FROM weather_forecasts_visual_crossing
	WHERE location_name = '${location_name}')

INSERT INTO ${table} (
	prediction_date,
	prediction_time,
	date,
	time,
	condition,
	longitude,
	latitude,
	location_name,
	snow, 
	ice, 
	lightning,
	technology
) VALUES (
	'${prediction_date}'
	,'${prediction_time}'
	,'NULL'

	,${longitude:replaceNull('NULL')}
	,${latitude:replaceNull('NULL')}
